snippet.title: 'The Librarian' Trailer. A short game by Octavi Navarro.
snippet.description:
Get my new short game 'The Librarian' for free on itch.io! :D
https://octavinavarro.itch.io/the-librarian

I hope you enjoy it!! :)

If you liked this game and want to help on the creation of future titles, please consider becoming a patron:

https://www.patreon.com/octavinavarro  

Every little bit helps! :)

Prints of my works are for sale here: http://www.redbubble.com/people/pixelshuh

Also, you can follow me on:
Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/OctaviNavarro
Facebook - http://www.facebook.com/octavinavarroAG
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/octavi_navarro
